      <h2 class="font-black text-[clamp(30px,3vw,40px)]"> Need Assistance in IBC Proceedings? </h2> 
      <p class="max-w-[880px] mx-auto mt-3 mb-7 text-[16.5px] leading-[1.85]"> Legalx24 provides comprehensive legal support in insolvency and bankruptcy matters before NCLT, ensuring strategic, compliant, and result-oriented representation. </p> 
